Package: krode
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Delete onboard recordings from Rode Interview PRO on Linux
 krode sends a vendor-specific HID command to the Rode Interview PRO
 wireless microphone transmitter to delete all onboard recordings.
 This functionality is normally only available through Rode Central,
 Rode's proprietary Windows/macOS software.
 .
 The protocol was reverse-engineered from USB HID traffic captures.
